    "PARAMORPHOUS": "Relating to paramorphism; exhibiting paramorphism.",
    "PARAMOUNT": "Having the highest rank or jurisdiction; superior to allothers; chief; supreme; preëminent; as, a paramount duty. \"A traitorparamount.\" Bacon. Lady paramount (Archery), the lady making the bestscore.-- Lord paramount, the king.",
