    "PARCHEDNESS": "The state of being parched.",
    "PARCHEESI": "See Pachisi.",
    "PARCHESI": "See Pachisi.",
    "PARCHING": "Scorching; burning; drying. \"Summer's parching heat.\" Shak.-- Parch\"ing*ly, adv.",
