    "PARENESIS": "Exhortation. [R.]",
    "PARENTAGE": "Descent from parents or ancestors; parents or ancestorsconsidered with respect to their rank or character; extraction;birth; as, a man of noble parentage. \"Wilt thou deny thy parentage\"Shak.Though men esteem thee low of parentage. Milton.",
