    "PLEASURABLE": "Capable of affording pleasure or satisfaction; gratifying;abounding in pleasantness or pleasantry.Planting of orchards is very . . . pleasurable. Bacon.O, sir, you are very pleasurable. B. Jonson.-- Pleas\"ur*a*ble*ness, n.-- Pleas\"ur*a*bly, adv.",
