    "PRE-": "A prefix denoting priority (of time, place, or rank); as,precede, to go before; precursor, a forerunner; prefix, to fix orplace before; preëminent eminent before or above others. Pre- issometimes used intensively, as in prepotent, very potent. [Writtenalso præ-.]",
